---

LOGIN PAGE - /login
Access: Public

Submit valid credentials - Enter email and password for any seeded user - Redirects Admin to /admin, Supplier to /supplier, others to /home
Submit invalid credentials - Wrong email or password - Flash error: Invalid email or password.
Submit empty fields - Leave email or password blank - Flash error: Please enter both email and password.
Click Back to Public Site - Link at bottom of form - Redirects to /index

---

PUBLIC PAGE - /index
Access: Public, no login required

View game calendar - Page loads and monthly calendar renders - Shows all upcoming games with red highlights on game dates
Navigate calendar months - Click the left and right arrow buttons - Calendar re-renders for previous or next month
Click a game date - Click a highlighted game cell - Game details appear in the details box below showing opponent, date, time, and location
View team players table - Scroll to Team Players section - Shows first 8 active players with jersey number, name, position, year, and status
Newsletter signup form - Enter email and click Subscribe - UI interaction only, no backend connection
Click Login button - Hero section login button - Redirects to /login

---

ADMIN DASHBOARD - /home
Access: Admin only

View dashboard stats - Page load - Displays total players, injured and active count, upcoming games, next game info, inventory count, pending orders, total revenue, total expenses, net balance, projected expenses, budget variance, and recent activity
Click Roster Player Information button - Button in System Modules card - Navigates to /roster
Click Scheduling and Notifications button - Button in System Modules card - Navigates to /schedule
Click Inventory Management button - Button in System Modules card - Navigates to /equipment
Click Financial Reporting button - Button in System Modules card - Navigates to /finances
Click Alumni Portal button - Button in System Modules card - Navigates to /alumni
Click Newsletter Management button - Button in System Modules card - Navigates to /newsletters
Change Password via navbar modal - Click Change Password in navbar - Opens modal with current, new, and confirm password fields
Submit change password with valid data - Fill in correct current password plus matching new password of 6 or more characters - Flash success: Password changed successfully.
Submit change password with wrong current password - Enter incorrect current password - Flash error: Current password is incorrect.
Submit change password with mismatched new passwords - New and confirm passwords differ - Flash error: New passwords do not match.
Submit change password with too short new password - New password under 6 characters - Flash error: New password must be at least 6 characters.
Logout - Click Logout in navbar - Session cleared and redirect to /login with flash: You have been logged out.

