ROSTER MANAGEMENT - /roster
Access: Admin and Coach can edit, Player can view only

View roster table - Page load - Displays all players with jersey number, name, position, year, injured status, email, and phone
Search players - Type in search box - Filters rows live by name, position, or jersey number using client-side JavaScript
Add Player - Admin or Coach clicks Add Player, fills modal form, clicks Save Player - POST to /add_player, new user and player record created, flash: Player added successfully.
Add Player with missing required fields - Submit with blank name, position, year, or email - Flash error: Please fill in all required fields.
Edit Player - Click Edit on a row, modify fields, click Update Player - POST to /update_player/player_id, updates users and players tables, flash: Player updated successfully.
Delete Player - Click Delete on a row and confirm the dialog - POST to /delete_player/player_id, deletes user which cascades to player record, flash: Player deleted successfully.

---

SCHEDULING AND NOTIFICATIONS - /schedule
Access: Admin and Coach can edit, Player can view only

GAME SCHEDULE TAB

View scheduled games - Games tab on load - Shows all games where in_results is false as cards
View game details - Click View Details on a game card - Opens Event Detail modal with opponent, date, location, type, status, costs, and notes
Add Game - Click Add Game, fill modal, click Save Game - POST to /add_game, inserts into games table, flash: Game added successfully.
Add Game with missing fields - Submit with blank required fields - Flash error: Please fill in all required game fields.
Edit Game - Click Edit on a game card, modify fields, click Save Changes - POST to /edit_game/game_id, updates game record, flash: Game updated successfully.
Move to Results - Click Move to Results on a game card - POST to /move_game_to_results/game_id, sets in_results to true and status to Completed, game moves to Results tab
Delete Game - Click Delete and confirm in the modal - POST to /delete_game/game_id, deletes game and all related financial entries and projections, flash confirmation shown

PRACTICES TAB

View scheduled practices - Practices tab - Shows all practices where in_results is false
Add Practice - Click Add Practice, fill modal, click Save Practice - POST to /add_practice, inserts into practices table, flash: Practice added successfully.
Edit Practice - Click Edit on a practice card, modify fields, click Save Changes - POST to /edit_practice/practice_id, updates practice record, flash success shown
Move to Results - Click Move to Results - POST to /move_practice_to_results/practice_id, sets in_results to true and status to Completed
Delete Practice - Click Delete and confirm in the modal - POST to /delete_practice/practice_id, deletes practice and related financial data

RESULTS TAB

View completed games and practices - Results tab - Shows all games and practices with in_results set to true
Save game result - Enter actual cost and final score, click Save Result - POST to /update_game_results/game_id, updates actual_cost and final_score fields
Save practice result - Enter actual cost, click Save Result - POST to /update_practice_results/practice_id, updates actual_cost field

EMAIL NOTIFICATIONS TAB

View recent notifications - Emails tab - Displays static table of recent notifications, display only
Send Message modal - Click Send Message, fill form, click Send Message - 

