TEAM CALENDAR - /calendar
Access: Admin, Coach, Player

View calendar - Page load - Monthly calendar renders for current month with financial summary cards at the top
Navigate months - Click left or right arrow buttons - Calendar re-renders for previous or next month
Filter event types - Click Game, Practice, or Other Event filter pills - Toggles visibility of that event type on the calendar
Click event on calendar - Click a colored event pill - Opens Event Detail modal with event info and financial entries
Add financial entry to event - Click Add Revenue or Expense in the event modal - Opens Add Financial Entry modal
Save financial entry - Select type and category, enter amount, click Save Entry - Entry added to in-memory data and updates summary cards, note this is not persisted to the database from this page
Remove financial entry - Click the X next to an entry in the event modal - Removes from in-memory list and re-renders the calendar
View on Schedule - Click View on Schedule in event modal - Redirects to /schedule
Financial summary cards - Top of page - Shows total event revenue, total event expenses, and net balance reflecting database values plus any in-session additions

