ALUMNI PORTAL - /alumni
Access: Admin, Coach

View alumni cards - Alumni Records tab on load - Cards for each alumni showing name, class year, position, email, occupation, phone, and donation status
Search alumni - Type in search box - Client-side filter by name, class year, or occupation
Summary stats - Top cards - Shows total donations in dollars, active alumni count, and newsletter subscribers shown as 36
Add Alumni without donation - Click Add Alumni, fill form, select Has Not Donated, click Save Alumni - POST to /add_alumni, inserts alumni record only
Add Alumni with donation - Select Donated so donation fields appear, fill amount and date and message, click Save Alumni - Inserts alumni record plus donation record plus financial entry as Revenue under Donation category
Edit Alumni - Click Edit on an alumni card, modify fields, click Save Changes - POST to /edit_alumni/alumni_id, updates alumni record
Delete Alumni - Click Delete on an alumni card and confirm - POST to /delete_alumni/alumni_id, deletes alumni and all linked donation records
View Donation Summary tab - Click Donation Summary tab - Table of all donations with alumni name, year, amount, and message plus breakdown cards below
Newsletter modal - Click Newsletters button - Opens newsletter subscription modal, UI only, no backend

