NEWSLETTER MANAGEMENT - /newsletters
Access: Admin, Coach

View subscribers - Subscribers tab - Static table of 4 sample subscribers, display only, not from database
View past newsletters - Past Newsletters tab - Table of all newsletters from the database with date, title, content preview, and author
Create Newsletter - Click Create Newsletter, enter title and content, click Save Newsletter - POST to /add_newsletter, inserts into newsletters table linked to current user, flash success shown
Create Newsletter with missing fields - Submit with blank title or content - Flash error: Title and content are required.
Delete Newsletter - Click Delete on a newsletter row and confirm - POST to /delete_newsletter/newsletter_id, removes record, flash: Newsletter deleted.
Summary stats - Top cards - Total Subscribers shown as 36, Past Newsletters shown as 8, Latest Issue shown as Mar 2026, all static display values

